== Named refs ==

Names refs are supported <ref name="foo">named ref</ref>.
They can be reused <ref name="foo" />.

== Mediawiki inside refs ==

Refs can also have formatting <ref>''beautiful'' '''formatting'''</ref>.

They also support links <ref>Interesting [[article]]</ref>.

Even tables are supported <ref>
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! H1 !! H2
|-
| A || B
|}
</ref>.

